oks to reinvoke.\n\n12. **Metrics (staging/src/k8s.io/apiserver/pkg/admission/metrics/metrics.go)**: Decorators wrap plugins to emit admission metrics. The `WithStepMetrics()` decorator tracks admission timing and rejection reasons separately for mutating and validating phases.\n\nThe execution flow: API request → `Server.Config.AdmissionControl.Admit()` → reinvoker → chainAdmissionHandler → each mutating plugin in order → reinvoker re-invokes if needed → chainAdmissionHandler → each validating plugin (webhooks in parallel) → response allowed/rejected."
}

